rows.label: tlk9301301_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I want to be able to chat with
all kinds of new people!

rows.label: tlk9301301_01_msg0002
rows.name:
So if you're going somewhere,
I'd love it if you'd take me along.

rows.label: tlk9301301_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh, but I guess then I'd have less
chance to talk with the people here...

rows.label: tlk9301301_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Hmmm...that would be kind of
a shame too, in its own way!

rows.label: tlk9301301_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Whatever should I do?
You got any bright ideas, Driver?

rows.label: tlk9301301_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Oh, come to think of it, I haven't
had much chance to chat with you
lately either, have I?

rows.label: tlk9301301_01_msg0007
rows.name: While we're here, let's chat right now!

rows.label: tlk9301301_01_msg0008
rows.name:
Or, uh...are you busy with other stuff
right now? No time for chatting?

rows.label: tlk9301301_01_msg0009
rows.name:
Awww...
Well, we should totally chat some
other time! That's a promise, okay?!
